1. Test: patch_hop_size variieren
Parameter:
Sift hop_size: 5
Sift cell_size: 15
Sift n_visual_words: 200
Dimensionen Topic Raum 200
patch_hop_size: 10, 20, 25

Ergebnisse (in %)
patch_hop_size	mean_recall	mean_avg_precision	
10				20			12
20				22			11,9
25				19,4		10,3


2. Test: Dimensionen Topic Raum und Anzahl Visual Words (n_classes) variiert:
Sift hop_size: 5
Sift cell_size: 15
Sift n_visual_words: 1000, 1500
Dimension Topic Raum: 200, 500
patch_hop_size: 20

Ergebnisse (in %)
n_classes	Dimensionen Topic Raum	mean_recall	mean_avg_precision	
1000		200						28			28
1000		500						35,7		35,7
1500		200						24			28
1500		500						35,7		35,7



